metadata.name: Double Skulls
metadata.description:
Recently it has become obsessive. The need to create. I spend weekends making things, in patterns. 
Down to the detail if it’s too real, scrap it. Organic as plastic. It probably don’t matter what you have in your scrap book. Over and over. And over and over. And over and over. And over and over. And over and over. And over and over.
